{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_11_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 どうして忘れてたんだろ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、例のMV撮影の件なんだが\n制作会社と打ち合わせしてきたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ about that MV shoot…\nI had a meeting with the production company.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.737528197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\nそれで、どうなりましたか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much‚ {user}-san.\nSo‚ how did it go!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5472559929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.6344671249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "制作会社の人達も『Grab the BIG4』の\nあのステージを観て、感動したらしくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even the people at the production company\napparently were moved after seeing that stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回のMVは、愛にほぼ任せてくれるそうだ\nいい映像を作りたい、って凄くやる気だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they’ll mostly leave this MV in your hands‚ Ai.\nThey were really motivated‚ wanting to make a great video.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.8555553118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　……あの日のステージが\nそんな風に誰かの心を動かしていたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? …That day’s stage\nactually moved someone’s heart like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5278001149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "いいステージが出来たんだなって\n改めて実感しました。……嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel it again that we managed\nto create a good stage.… I’m so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2611334483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0885254859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "よし！　まずは企画書、でしたよね\nアイデアは沢山あるので、書き出してみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! First‚ the proposal‚ right?\nI have lots of ideas‚ so I’ll start writing them down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7944667816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、よろしく頼むよ。アイデアを出してもらったら\n企画書は俺がまとめておくから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ thanks. Once you’ve got the ideas‚\nI’ll organize the proposal myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.5767337798
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "お任せ下さい！　{user}さんと\n制作会社さんの期待に、ちゃーんと応えてみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me! I’ll meet the expectations of you‚ {user}-san‚\nand the production company properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5209291775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6337178866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6670506994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\nどうしたらいいんだろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…\nWhat should I do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5875958442,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1772.404155800004,
          "startTime": 69.36
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "愛、そろそろMVのアイデアが欲しいんだけど\n……な、何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ I need the MV ideas soon.\n…Uh‚ did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……\nいえ、何もないんですけど……それが問題というか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san…\nNo‚ it’s nothing… but that’s the problem…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0099765777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "そう、私には何もない……\nいや、何もないことはないんですけど……う～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I have nothing…\nWell‚ not exactly nothing‚ but… uhh~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4099765777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いて話を聞かせてくれ\nもしかして、MVの件で何か悩んでるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down and tell me.\nCould it be… you’re troubled about the MV?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9060243736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……実はMVのアイデアを\n沢山書き出してみたんですけど、全然しっくりこなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes… actually‚ the MV ideas…\nI wrote down lots‚ but nothing feels right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9382957775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ここに置いてあるのは……MVのアイデア帳か\n愛、良かったら見せてもらえるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… the MV idea notebook‚ huh?\nAi‚ can I take a look if it’s okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0999974568,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5717.617956799998,
          "startTime": 121.8176154136
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。例えば、このページを見て下さい\nここに書いてあるアイデアなんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. For example‚ look at this page.\nThese are the ideas written here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8676154136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ……「海辺や草原、街中を走り続ける私達」\n「ついでに、犬とか猫とか鳥とかも一緒に」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… “Running along the beach‚ fields‚ and streets.”\n“Also‚ dogs‚ cats‚ birds‚ all together.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "人だけじゃなくて、いろんな生き物と走ることで\n力強さを表現出来ると思ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By running with not just people but various creatures‚\nI thought we could express strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4215838749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "想像してみたよ。和みそう……だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I imagined it. Looks… calming‚ I guess.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3872992675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、凄くほんわかした動物ふれあい動画に\nなってしまう気がして、ボツにしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I felt it would just end up as\na super fluffy animal-interaction video… …so I scrapped it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4269352276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、スカイダイビングとかバンジージャンプとか\n未体験のことへの挑戦、っていうのも考えたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also considered skydiving‚ bungee jumping‚\nchallenges involving new experiences…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2936018943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "想像してみたら、楽しい体験VTRになる未来しか\n見えなくて……どう思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I imagined it‚ all I could see was\na fun experience video… What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4269352276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "同感だ。みんなの楽しそうな顔が思い浮かぶよ\n……どうやら行き詰まってるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree. I can picture everyone having fun.\n…Looks like you’re stuck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "MVで表現したいことが、あり過ぎるのかもしれません\nそのせいで、アイデアがまとまらないというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might have too many things I want to express in the MV.\nBecause of that‚ my ideas aren’t coming together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.3221927959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そうか……愛、この後オフだったよな\nちょっと俺に付き合ってもらえないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I see… Ai‚ you’re off later‚ right?\nCould you come with me for a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.6333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "はい、それは全然構いませんけど……\nはっ！　もしかして{user}さん",
      "translations": {
